openSUSE believes in choice and doesn't limit it. We also believe in making it easy for you to make decisions, and giving you the same seamless experience with openSUSE you'll get with any choices you make. We believe in adjusting your system to you, and no matter what route you take or what you try to achieve,
you're never alone with the openSUSE community. So make your choice, and choose openSUSE.

flowRoot.flowPara: A equipe Educacional do openSUSE se orgulha de apresentar o openSUSE Edu-Li-Fe (Linux para a Educao), baseado no openSUSE 11.3.
A imagem do Educaciobal Li-f-e uma "imagem iso" hbrida, pode ser usada para criar um DVD ao vivo (Live) ou um USB stick (Pendrive).
Esta verso inclui softwares selecionados cuidadosamente para estudantes, educadores e pais.
A seleo de software inclui tudo que necessrio para permitir que os computadores possam ser utilizados tanto para uso residencial como educacional.
